Package: MRDviz
Title: Visualization and Simulation of Minimal Residual Disease (MRD) Data
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Kwangbom", "Choi", , "kbchoi@abbvie.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application for visualizing and simulating Minimal Residual Disease (MRD) 
    data in clinical trials. Provides interactive visualization of longitudinal MRD measurements,
    survival analysis, and simulation capabilities for MRD trajectories.
